        <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Basket and decanter centrifuges differ in a variety of ways. In this section, we compare the typical specifications of these centrifuges.</p>
        <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">The following table compares the essential characteristics that affect centrifugal performance.</p>

